    <item>
      <title>英国家庭用水进一步紧张，水费或将上涨 36%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/uk-water-bills-to-rise-36-over-5-years-as-households-squeezed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来五年，英格兰和威尔士的水费将上涨 36%，这将给已经感受到高价压力的家庭带来更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/uk-water-bills-to-rise-36-over-5-years-as-households-squeezed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 07:19:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士河水务收益低于财务计划所需水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/thames-water-equity-investors-will-get-5-1-return-says-ofwat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公司的股权投资者将在未来五年内获得 5.1% 的回报，这对于这家负债累累、努力维持运营的公司来说是一个关键的监管标志。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/thames-water-equity-investors-will-get-5-1-return-says-ofwat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 07:10:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾下调基准利率，将继续适度宽松</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/philippines-cuts-rates-extending-easing-as-inflation-on-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾央行连续第三次将政策利率下调四分之一个百分点，并表示在通胀保持在目标水平且经济增长放缓的情况下，打算维持适度的宽松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/philippines-cuts-rates-extending-easing-as-inflation-on-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 06:57:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国与国民养老金将外汇互换规模扩大至 650 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/south-korea-national-pension-to-expand-fx-swap-to-65-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行与韩国国民年金公团达成协议，扩大货币互换协议的规模和期限，此举或有助于减缓韩元的下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/south-korea-national-pension-to-expand-fx-swap-to-65-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中石化称中国汽油需求将继续下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/china-s-gasoline-demand-to-fall-quickly-from-2025-sinopec-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最大的炼油商表示，该国的汽油需求去年已达到峰值，随着电动汽车普及步伐加快，汽油需求将加速下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/china-s-gasoline-demand-to-fall-quickly-from-2025-sinopec-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 04:19:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>策略师称上田诚观点鸽派，日元逼近 160</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-s-outlook-worsens-as-boj-skips-rate-hike-strategists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[策略师们表示，日本央行放弃可能的加息，且行长上田一夫表示央行并不急于加息，日元兑美元汇率似乎将跌破 160。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-s-outlook-worsens-as-boj-skips-rate-hike-strategists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 04:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受上田评论影响，日元下跌逾 1%，至 7 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-weakens-past-155-against-dollar-after-boj-stands-pat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行维持利率不变之后，日元周四突破了更多里程碑，兑美元汇率下跌逾 1%，至 7 月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/yen-weakens-past-155-against-dollar-after-boj-stands-pat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 02:56:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储政策转变对货币造成冲击，亚洲央行开始反击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储采取强硬降息措施后，亚洲各国央行都面临着艰难的决定 — — 是采取代价高昂的措施反击美元走强，还是袖手旁观，看着本国货币贬值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/asian-currencies-tumble-as-fed-s-hawkish-cut-jolts-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 01:12:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储降息后欧洲股市跟随全球股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储的鹰派立场震动了市场，欧洲股市也跟随亚洲和美国股市下跌。由于日本央行维持借贷成本不变，日元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 22:59:17 GMT</pubDate>
